column2: SELECT     m.name AS id , m.ID_ra AS ra, m.ID_dec AS dec,     n.objid, n.distance, n.deVRad_i, n.deVRad_g, n.deVRad_r    o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.Marisa2 AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ID_ra, m.ID_dec, #) AS n     JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
